trans-unit.source: Represents the core properties of a <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer kjerner egenskaper for en <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets the category of the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, henter eller angir kategorien av den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The Category value is typically used as part of the application [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] to create labels for navigation controls.
trans-unit.target: Kategori-verdien brukes vanligvis som en del av programmet [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] til å opprette etiketter for Sidenavigeringskontrollene vises.

trans-unit.source: The category of the content that is contained in the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Kategorien av innholdet i den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets a value that represents the status of the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, henter eller angir en verdi som representerer statusen for den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Example ContentStatus values include "Draft", "Reviewed", and "Final".
trans-unit.target: Eksempel ContentStatus verdier inkluderer "Kladd", "Kontrollert" og "Endelig".

trans-unit.source: The status of the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref> content.
trans-unit.target: Statusen for den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref> innhold.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets a value that represents the type of content that is contained in the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, henter eller angir en verdi som representerer innholdstypen som ligger i den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Example ContentType values include "Whitepaper", "Security Bulletin", and "Exam".
trans-unit.target: Eksempel ContentType verdier inkluderer "Tekniske beskrivelsen", "Security Update" og "Eksamen".

trans-unit.source: This ContentType property is distinct from [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-mime-md.md)] content types as defined in RFC 2616.
trans-unit.target: Denne ContentType-egenskapen er forskjellig fra [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_mime](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-mime-md.md)] innholdstyper som er definert i RFC 2616.

trans-unit.source: The type of content that is contained in the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Innholdstypen som ligger i den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets the date and time the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref> was created.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, henter eller angir datoen og klokkeslettet den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref> ble opprettet.

trans-unit.source: The date and time the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref> was initially created.
trans-unit.target: Datoen og klokkeslettet den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref> opprinnelig ble opprettet.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets a value that identifies the individual or entity that created the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref> and its content.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, henter eller angir en verdi som identifiserer person eller enhet som opprettes av <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref> og innholdet.

trans-unit.source: The individual or entity that created the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref> and its content.
trans-unit.target: Person eller enhet som opprettes av <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref> og innholdet.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, gets or sets a description of the content contained in the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, henter eller angir en beskrivelse av innholdet i den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The Description may include but is not limited to: an abstract, table of contents, reference to a graphical representation of content, or a free-text account of the content.
trans-unit.target: Beskrivelsen kan omfatte, men er ikke begrenset til: en abstrakt, innholdsfortegnelse, referanse til en grafisk fremstilling av innhold, eller en gratis fulltekst-konto på innholdet.

trans-unit.source: A description of the content contained in the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En beskrivelse av innholdet i den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties"></xref> instance.
trans-unit.target: Frigir alle ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties"> </xref> forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: Call Dispose when you are finished using the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>.
trans-unit.target: Kall avhending når du er ferdig med <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: Opp fjerningsmetoden forlater den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>i en ubrukelig tilstand.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>

trans-unit.source: After calling Dispose, you must release all references to the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Etter å avhending, må du frigi alle referanser til den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>Slik saneringsoppsamlingen kan gjenvinne minnet som den <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>ble bruker.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [Rydder opp uforvaltede ressurser](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [implementere metoden fjerne](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Alltid kall fjerne før du slipper siste referanse til <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Ellers ressurser den bruker vil ikke bli frigjort før saneringsoppsamling kall av <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>objektets `Finalize` metode.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties"></xref> instance and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Frigir uforvaltede ressursene som brukes av den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties"> </xref> serverforekomsten og eventuelt frigir administrerte ressurser.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by the public `Dispose()`method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles av offentlig `Dispose()`metoden og <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>metode.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with the `disposing` parameter set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: `Dispose()`Aktiverer den beskyttede `Dispose(Boolean)` metoden med den `disposing` parameteren satt til `true`.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>aktiverer `Dispose` med `disposing` satt til `false`.</xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the `disposing` parameter is true, this method releases all resources held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties> references.
trans-unit.target: Når den `disposing` -parameteren er SANN, denne metoden Frigjør alle ressurser holdes av administrerte objekter som denne <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>referanser.</xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackageProperties>

trans-unit.source: This method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden starter den `Dispose()` metode for hver referert objekt.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>å frigjøre både administrerte og uforvaltede ressurser. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> frigi bare uforvaltede ressurser.

trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, henter eller angir en verdi som identifiserer utvetydig den <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"> </xref> og innholdet.

trans-unit.source: A delimited set of keywords to support searching and indexing the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.Package"></xref> and content.

trans-unit.source: The Revision property indicates the number of changed saves or revisions.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen revisjon angir hvor mange endret lagrer eller endringer.

trans-unit.source: The application is responsible for updating the Revision property value after each revision.
